high_descs: Walk towards the wall, then hang a left and walk across the room, hang a right and walk up to the black dresser.
Pick up the pen off of the dresser.
Turn left and walk towards the window, then turn right to face the glass bowl on the dresser.
Put the pen in the glass bowl on the dresser.
Pick up the glass bowl with the pen in it.
Walk across the room and around the bed to the small black end table in between the bed and wall.
Put the glass bowl with the pen in it on the small black end table to the right of the lamp.
